(165, 'Computer Networks', 'Network Layers', 'Transport layer protocols deals with ____________', 'application to application communication', 'process to process communication', 'node to node communication', ' man to man communication', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', '2021-11-16', 'B', 1),
(166, 'Computer Networks', 'Network Layers', 'Which of the following is a transport layer protocol?', ' stream control transmission protocol', 'internet control message protocol', 'neighbor discovery protocol', 'dynamic host configuration protocol', 'The Stream Control Transmission Protocol (SCTP) is a transport layer protocol used in networking system where streams of data are to be continuously transmitted between two connected network nodes. Some of the other transport layer protocols are RDP, RUDP, TCP, DCCP, UDP', 'No', 'No', 'No', '2021-11-16', 'A', 1),
(167, 'Artificial Intelligence', 'Introduction', ' First AI programming language is?', 'LISP', 'IPL', 'FORTRON', 'BASIC', 'The first practical and still most widely used AI programming language is the functional language Lisp developed by John McCarthy in the late 1950s.', 'Clifford Shaw of the Rand Corporation and Herbert Simon of Carnegie Mellon University developed their Information Processing Language (IPL), a computer language tailored for AI programming. ', 'No', 'No', '2021-11-16', 'B', 1),
